    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><blockquote><p>HVV期间闲来无事，搭建一个静态博客放一些自己的笔记和碎碎念。那么第一篇文章就记录搭建这个博客遇到的一些问题吧。</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="npm安装hexo卡住"><a href="#npm安装hexo卡住" class="headerlink" title="npm安装hexo卡住"></a>npm安装hexo卡住</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i hexo-cli -g一直卡住爬墙也不行，配置国内源解决：</span><br><span class="line">npm config set registry https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="hexo-baidu-url-submit插件报错"><a href="#hexo-baidu-url-submit插件报错" class="headerlink" title="hexo-baidu-url-submit插件报错"></a>hexo-baidu-url-submit插件报错</h2><p><img src="/2020/09/19/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/image-20200919010133612.png" alt="log"></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">该插件的功能是推送到百度让百度收录此网站。但需要在配置站长平台账号等，不配置会报如上错误。目前只打算当做我的笔记网站，所以删除此插件。</span><br><span class="line">参考：https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;hexojs&#x2F;hexo&#x2F;issues&#x2F;2402</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Markdown中插入图片问题"><a href="#Markdown中插入图片问题" class="headerlink" title="Markdown中插入图片问题"></a>Markdown中插入图片问题</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1、图床方式</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2、图片存放本地方式</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">注：直接安装插件的方式：npm install hexo-asset-image --save会导致图片无法加载</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">需要通过如下方式安装可正常使用</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">npm install https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;xcodebuild&#x2F;hexo-asset-image.git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">参考：https:&#x2F;&#x2F;leay.net&#x2F;2019&#x2F;12&#x2F;25&#x2F;hexo&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HVV期间闲来无事，搭建一个静态博客放一些自己的笔记和碎碎念。那么第一篇文章就记录搭建这个博客遇到的一些问题吧。&lt;/p&gt;
